<!DOCTYPE HTML><html><head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>Edward Professional Advisors - Mario Soldivier's Biography</title><link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.ico" /><meta name="description" content="Write description here."><meta name="keywords" content="insert, keywords, here"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"><link rel="stylesheet" href="mario-soldivier.css" type="text/css" media="screen"><link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:400,700" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"></head><body><div class="container"><div id="header"><div id="i1"><a href="index.php"><img src="images/banner.gif" style="width: 100%; height: auto;"></a></div></div><div id="i2"><div id="i3"><div class="page-title">Mario Soldivier, MBA<br></div><div id="i5"><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="images/mario-soldivier1469470640.jpg" data-pin-nopin="true"></div><div id="i6"></div><div id="i7"><div>Mario Soldivier is an expert in Latin American markets. His methodical approach to identifying and evaluating overseas business opportunities helps companies maximize earnings, minimize losses, and save valuable time.</div><div><br></div><div>Mr. Soldivier is a native of Argentina, where he earned his BA in Industrial Administration from the prestigious Universidad Tecnológica Nacional. He then emigrated to America where he earned his MBA from California State University, Fullerton.</div></div><div id="i8"><img src="images/MS3.jpg" style="width: 100%; height: auto;"></div><div id="i9"><b>If your organization is thinking about entering the Latin American market for the first time or wants to increase its current sales or presence in Latin America, we can help you.<br></b><div><b><br></b></div><div><b>Here are some of our deliverables:</b></div><div><div><ul><li><span style="line-height: 1.5; background-color: inherit;"><b>Detailed Intelligence Reports:</b> Provides you with a ranking of the countries, industries and applications where your organization should focus its priorities and resources, as well as the most viable segments and niches.</span><br></li><li><span style="line-height: 1.5; background-color: inherit;"><b>Distribution Setup:</b> Assistance with setting up profitable and efficient distribution networks in the selected countries.</span><br></li><li><span style="line-height: 1.5; background-color: inherit;"><b>Sales Leads:</b> Lists of qualified sales leads (comprised of the most important potential buyers in selected countries or regions).</span><br></li><li><span style="line-height: 1.5; background-color: inherit;"><b>Transaction Closing:</b> Assistance and strategies to convert prospects to paying clients, including contacting, interviewing and following up with the decision makers of major accounts.</span><br></li><li><span style="line-height: 1.5; background-color: inherit;"><b>Representation:</b> Attending trade shows in the region and representing your products or services to potential buyers.</span><br></li></ul></div></div></div><div id="i10"><div style="background-color: inherit;"><span style="line-height: 1.5; background-color: inherit;"><b>We Have a Region-Wide Presence</b></span><br><br><span style="line-height: 1.5; background-color: inherit;">In addition to our headquarters in the United States, we have offices in Brazil (Rio de Janeiro) and Argentina (Buenos Aires), staffed with native speakers. See the image to view the sub-regions that our offices cover.</span><br></div></div><div id="i11"><img src="images/MS2.gif" style="width: 100%; height: auto;"></div><div id="i12"><div style="background-color: inherit;"><b>We Guarantee Your Satisfaction</b><br><br>We're so confident in our ability to add value, that we'll run a test market for your organization. We'll choose a country and then conduct an analysis to determine if your product is best suited for that market. You'll be able to monitor the process and contact any potential distributor or buyer that we use for your organization. If you are not completely satisfied, we'll return your fee.<br></div></div><div style="clear: both;"></div></div></div><div id="i13"><div id="i14">CONTACT INFO</div><div id="i15">mariosoldivier@edwardprofessionaladvisors.com</div><div id="i16">PHONE:<b> 714-418-4812</b><br></div><div id="i17">FAX:<b> 714-917-7089</b><br></div></div><div id="footer"><div id="i19">© 2016 - EDWARD PROFESSIONAL ADVISORS<div>info@edwardpa.com</div><div>888-858-9510<br></div></div></div></div></body></html>